CUTS N CURLS RAILS APP NOTES

Domain - Hair Salon/Barbershop - Can be adapted to suit both

Models
------
USER
  has a name
  has a username
  has a password
    password is encrypted
  
  has a role
    client
    hair stylist
    manager
    admin

  has many appointments

APPOINTMENT
  has a time
  has a date
  belongs to a user